title: TopChef: Does a Bear Schnitzel in the Woods?
description:
This week on Top Chef, the contestants must audition from Tasty.com, and after that it's a good ol' fashioned German party. DAS FLAVORS! Come listen to our recap!

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.
